                                <span>Yuval Noah Harari</span>
                                <div class="badge-premium">Mới</div>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-6 col-md-3">
                            <a href="/Book/Detail/2" class="book-card">
                                <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTv98FnKFIl1mWp2oF2YjMiVb9XCxuKExy0Gw&s">
                                <h6>12 Rules for Life</h6>
                                <span>Jordan Peterson</span>
                                <div class="badge-premium">Hot</div>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-6 col-md-3">
                            <a href="/Book/Detail/3" class="book-card">
                                <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSgGpv1ctGy0hjdg5Htgfh7PDosTEN5kkDNrw&s">
