                            </a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-6 col-md-3">
                            <a href="/Book/Detail/4" class="book-card">
                                <img src="https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/71F4+7rk2eL._UF894,1000_QL80_.jpg">
                                <h6>Atomic Habits</h6>
                                <span>James Clear</span>
